    "name": "Layered Loop层叠环道",
    "steam_appid": 3229820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >详情介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《层垒环道》是一款极简塔防游戏。游戏中的塔在达成条件后会自动升级获得伤害的增加或产能的提升。游戏中的塔在达到一定等级后可以吞噬相邻的key建筑实现进化，获得新能力或数值的大幅度提升。可以在塔上再建塔，就像搭建高楼一样，所有的层的效果都会保留。在塔的高度达到5层后，会根据塔的构成获得不同的全局增幅。在有限的位置上搭建无限的塔抵御源源不断的敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个圆环世界的中心，有一个活着的核心，敌人们源源不断地冲向它。你的使命只有一个：构筑防线并守护它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >环道</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 块地块完美排列成一个圆形。在地块上建造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心机制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模块堆叠与奇迹（五层奇观）</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/8e7ebc3cdfe2c956b66747ca26b732df.poster.avif?t=1771581499\" width=614 height=702 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/8e7ebc3cdfe2c956b66747ca26b732df.webm?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/8e7ebc3cdfe2c956b66747ca26b732df.mp4?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >堆叠——每一座塔在英雄经过一定次数并达到一定等级后，允许其像地块一样往上搭建新的建筑，付出的代价是除了最上层建筑，下面的建筑都将失去成长能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奇迹——1层，2层...5层，当堆叠达到5层后，奇迹会降临在这个5层建筑上，为场上所有建筑带来强大的全局增幅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进化系统</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/470967eafb30fd86e087d419018d9459.poster.avif?t=1771581499\" width=410 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/470967eafb30fd86e087d419018d9459.webm?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/470967eafb30fd86e087d419018d9459.mp4?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座建筑都有三个进化阶段，每一次进化都需要达到一定等级并消耗相邻的Key建筑，换取的是更强的力量</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <i>一阶：初生形态。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>  二阶：强化变体。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>  三阶：终极之形。超越凡俗。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>协同与共鸣</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >协同——各种建筑能够互相影响，能产出数据能的数据站S，能将数据能转换成子弹的防御塔D，能使周围建筑射速加快的B，能使下层建筑伤害指数级提高的A等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共鸣——英雄经过时，不同的建筑会产生不同的效果，经过S会获得数据能，经过D会给D补充数据能，经过L会获得免费的抽卡次数等。共鸣也是堆叠的必要条件之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>英雄之旅</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/7ecd27433e056d36a80e4b1b2e0b67aa.poster.avif?t=1771581499\" width=680 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/7ecd27433e056d36a80e4b1b2e0b67aa.webm?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/7ecd27433e056d36a80e4b1b2e0b67aa.mp4?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个英雄都有不同的主动技能和被动技能，不同的技能适用不同的发展策略。自带武器的英雄也就意味着前期可以不需要防御塔，可以全力发展经济。经济性英雄则可以侧重于防御部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总计20+英雄，不同的英雄可以带来不同的游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建筑族系</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 种核心建筑，24 种独特的个性：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生成塔（S 型）：</strong>汇聚能量。增幅同伴。你的经济支柱。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>炮塔（D 型）：</strong>消灭威胁。随进化而强大。你对抗混沌的拳头。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>物流塔（L 型）：</strong>交易资源。开启通道。助力无尽扩张。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>透镜（A 型）：</strong>放大一切。力量的倍增器。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>还有 20 种更深层次的建筑：</strong>等待你去发掘它们的奥秘……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/c6c49064930dbc0c278aa4ab020e8fd0.poster.avif?t=1771581499\" width=336 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/c6c49064930dbc0c278aa4ab020e8fd0.webm?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/c6c49064930dbc0c278aa4ab020e8fd0.mp4?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次游戏都是独特的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次失败都教会你新的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次成功都验证你的战术。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为什么选择《层垒环道》？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/e53c871043ddc0624d672563e1dec5c4.poster.avif?t=1771581499\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/e53c871043ddc0624d672563e1dec5c4.webm?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/e53c871043ddc0624d672563e1dec5c4.mp4?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">这不是一场关乎反射神经的游戏。</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这是一场关乎思维的对话。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">这不是一场充满随机性的游戏。</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这是一场关乎发展与策略的游戏。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">这不是一场充满磨炼感的游戏。</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这是一场关乎优雅与美学的艺术。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在视觉噪音充斥的世界里，《层垒环道》用低语诉说故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在复杂性泛滥的时代，《层垒环道》揭示秩序的本质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>站在中心。有意识地建造。守护你的核心。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让奇迹为你证明。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/8007a3a806fc2d5a74a9285d7a0828a4.poster.avif?t=1771581499\" width=940 height=628 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/8007a3a806fc2d5a74a9285d7a0828a4.webm?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3229820/extras/8007a3a806fc2d5a74a9285d7a0828a4.mp4?t=1771581499\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
